{"type":"message","id":"05615bb0","parentId":"f736fd97","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:32:50.549Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978 空闲检测自主学习] 请检测当前是否有活跃对话（查询 sessions_list）。如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息），则执行自主学习：\n\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n如果有活跃对话，直接回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 28th, 2026 — 12:32 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-28 04:32 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774672370546}}
{"type":"message","id":"13f10ce5","parentId":"05615bb0","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:33:02.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job asking me to check for active sessions and if none are active, perform autonomous learning about relevant industries. Let me check the sessions list first.","thinkingSignature":"851aa1660d4d525cd19b78f5ff593b222a59a653e0dd092b0906bb205709f0f8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0kglt3hy5gy1_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":72,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":44362,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0000864,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0.00002064,"total":0.0014675699999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774672370547}}
